            "answer_text": "Simply click onto the \u201cview playlist\u201d option, and drag your desired sample into the playlist, then go to the top left hand side of the Playlist and there should be two radio button options being \u201cZ-cross\u201d or \u201cStretch\u201d, just click on the \u201cstretch\u201d option and then go back to your sample and just drag it like you were trying to shorten it or make it longer, and instead of that it will now stretch it. ",
